					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1932" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C579&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1159&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1545&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=193%2C146&amp;ssl=1 193w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 是什麼情況能讓上一秒露出笑容的狗狗秒變成凝重的臉呢？近日一位飼主帶著家中兩隻哈 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/13/%e8%81%bd%e5%88%b0%e8%a6%81%e6%89%93%e9%87%9d%e7%a7%92%e8%ae%8a%e8%87%89%ef%bc%81%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%80%e7%a7%92%e7%87%a6%e7%ac%91%e5%8f%8d%e5%b7%ae%e8%90%8c%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e7%ac%91%e7%bf%bb/">聽到要打針秒變臉！前一秒燦笑反差萌讓網友笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1932" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C579&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1159&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1545&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=193%2C146&amp;ssl=1 193w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/joenomias-m-de-jong-zhYy10qCzdw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>是什麼情況能讓上一秒露出笑容的狗狗秒變成凝重的臉呢？近日一位飼主帶著家中兩隻哈士奇前往獸醫院接種疫苗，過程中狗狗的神情就像搭上雲霄飛車般，巨大的反差萌引發網友熱烈討論，讓人忍俊不禁。&nbsp;</p>



<p>這兩隻天真無邪的狗狗分別叫做「Sylvia」與「Chanter」，牠們從小就是性格活潑的哈士奇，總是露出燦爛般的笑容陪伴在主人身邊，飼主也特別紀錄下牠們即將施打疫苗的前一天的快樂模樣，似乎全然不知隔日即將面對的挑戰。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1627" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nataliia-kvitovska-t64RjBExKCQ-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C1627&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-240799" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nataliia-kvitovska-t64RjBExKCQ-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nataliia-kvitovska-t64RjBExKCQ-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nataliia-kvitovska-t64RjBExKCQ-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1152%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1152w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nataliia-kvitovska-t64RjBExKCQ-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/nataliia-kvitovska-t64RjBExKCQ-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=110%2C146&amp;ssl=1 110w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「Sylvia」與「Chanter」從小性格活潑，總是露出燦爛笑容<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>直到隔天當飼主帶著愛犬抵達獸醫院排隊時， 「 Sylvia」與「Chanter」才意識到事情不對勁，牠們漸漸地察覺到即將發生的事，神情瞬間變得凝重，同時略為緊張地緊盯著外頭的街景，彷彿在計算逃跑的可能性。&nbsp;</p>



<p>雖然狗狗依舊乖巧地坐在原地，但那份「想回家」的渴望幾乎寫滿整張臉，哈士奇的有趣反應引起許多飼主的共鳴，不少人紛紛留言表示「跟我家的狗一樣」、「也太真實」、「終究還是錯付」、「有點心疼又好好笑」、「來都來了」、「忍一下就結束了」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/13/%e8%81%bd%e5%88%b0%e8%a6%81%e6%89%93%e9%87%9d%e7%a7%92%e8%ae%8a%e8%87%89%ef%bc%81%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%80%e7%a7%92%e7%87%a6%e7%ac%91%e5%8f%8d%e5%b7%ae%e8%90%8c%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e7%ac%91%e7%bf%bb/">聽到要打針秒變臉！前一秒燦笑反差萌讓網友笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
