		<title>貓咪每天「舔毛」竟花這麼久！這習慣竟與健康息息相關</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/12/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e6%af%8f%e5%a4%a9%e3%80%8c%e8%88%94%e6%af%9b%e3%80%8d%e7%ab%9f%e8%8a%b1%e9%80%99%e9%ba%bc%e4%b9%85%ef%bc%81%e9%80%99%e7%bf%92%e6%85%a3%e7%ab%9f%e8%88%87%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e6%81%af/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 12 Aug 2025 04:15:56 +0000</pubDate>
